
=Bio=

Ziri Rideaux is the Chief Strategy Officer of [https://2gather.one/ 2Gather]. She has been a political analyst and foreign correspondent for German television for over 20 years, covering conflicts in Afghanistan, Iraq, Bosnia, Rwanda and South Africa among others. She focuses on the challenges to developing democracies under pressure from international corporations and outside foreign interests. She is a serial entrepreneur, having started a successful multinational photography agency and innovated a first-of-its-kind digital distribution system. She has also started service companies providing industry-leading customer satisfaction through the adoption of virtualization and dematerialization strategies. Ziri has two master’s degrees from Munich University, in political science and investigative journalism.

